Looking at the cfg looks like a small change was made the minislab has 

    MODULE{    name = ModuleKISItem    volumeOverride = 100    stackable = true    allowAttachOnStatic = true}MODULE{    name = ModuleKISPartStatic    breakForce = 10}

 and KIS concreteBase is 

    	MODULE	{		name = ModuleKISItem		volumeOverride = 100		stackable = true		allowPartAttach = 2		allowStaticAttach = 1		staticAttachBreakForce = 10	}

EDIT- And KAS Pylon has 

    	MODULE	{		name = ModuleKISItem		volumeOverride = 150		stackable = true		allowStaticAttach = 1		staticAttachBreakForce = 10	}

